# BLOG TEMPLATE SYSTEM IMPLEMENTATION

## PROJECT CONTEXT
Premium minimal elegant editorial website "Mirellé Inspo" (nail art/beauty content). Mobile-first responsive design. Strict adherence to provided Tailwind config and global CSS - use ONLY existing fonts and colors, NO new ones. NO reference to old BlogPost.tsx design - completely new minimal editorial aesthetic.

## FONTS (from provided config)
- **Larken**: Article titles and component headings ONLY
- **General Sans**: Everything else (body, buttons, navigation, product text, meta info, "READ MORE" heading)

## GOAL
Implement 4 distinct blog post templates with reusable components. Zero breaking changes - backward compatible. Completely new minimal editorial design, no old component styling.

## CURRENT SYSTEM
- Route: `src/app/blog/[slug]/page.tsx`
- Data: `src/lib/blog.ts` (fetches MD files, parses frontmatter)
- Types: `src/types/blog.ts`
- Content: `src/content/blogs/*.md`
- Existing component: `src/components/Blog/BlogPost.tsx`

