### TEMPLATES TO CREATE (4 new)

All templates located in: `src/app/blog/[slug]/templates/`

**Common template structure (all 4 templates):**

```tsx
<Template>
  {/* Meta Section */}
  <div className="text-center">
    <p>{category}</p>
    <h1>{title}</h1>
    <p>BY {author}</p>
    <p>{date}</p>
  </div>

  {/* Hero Image (varies by template) */}
  
  {/* Breadcrumbs component */}
  <Breadcrumbs />
  
  {/* Article content with manual component placement */}
  <article className="max-w-[720px] mx-auto">
    {/* First content paragraphs */}
    <div dangerouslySetInnerHTML={{ __html: firstSection }} />
    
    {/* Manual component insertions */}
    <ImageCarousel images={post.carouselImages} />
    
    {/* More content */}
    <div dangerouslySetInnerHTML={{ __html: middleSection }} />
    
    <ProductGrid products={post.products} layout="dual" />
    
    {/* More content */}
    <div dangerouslySetInnerHTML={{ __html: moreContent }} />
    
    <InlineNewsletter />
    
    {/* Remaining content */}
    <div dangerouslySetInnerHTML={{ __html: remainingContent }} />
  </article>
  
  {/* End sections (same order for all templates) */}
  <AboutEEAT />
  <FinalNewsletter />
  <ReadMoreSection currentSlug={post.slug} />
</Template>
```

