- H2 in content: Larken 36px/26px mobile, margin-top 48px/32px mobile
- H3 in content: Larken 28px/22px mobile, margin-top 36px/24px mobile
- Images in content: Rounded corners, shadow, margin 48px/32px mobile vertical
- Use brand colors ONLY from Tailwind config
