**1. CenterTemplate.tsx**
- Meta section at top (category, title, author, date) - centered
- Hero: Full-width centered image, natural aspect ratio (no crop/fill), max-width 1200px, rounded corners, shadow
- Breadcrumbs below hero
- Content: Centered column, max-width 720px
- Manual component placement:
  - ImageCarousel after ~20% of content
  - ProductGrid (dual) after ~40% of content
  - InlineNewsletter after ~60% of content
- End sections: AboutEEAT → FinalNewsletter → ReadMoreSection

**2. SplitLeftTemplate.tsx**
- Meta section at top (category, title, author, date) - centered
- Desktop hero section: 50/50 split, equal height
  - Left 50%: Hero image container
    - Image: object-fit contain (shows full image, no crop)
    - Vertically and horizontally centered in container
    - Background: subtle color from config if image doesn't fill
  - Right 50%: Empty space or subtle background
- Mobile hero: Image centered with 24px padding, NOT full-width, natural aspect ratio
- Breadcrumbs below hero
- Content: Centered column, max-width 720px
- Same manual component placement as CenterTemplate
- End sections same order

**3. SplitRightTemplate.tsx**
- Meta section at top (category, title, author, date) - centered
- Desktop hero section: 50/50 split, equal height
  - Left 50%: Empty space or subtle background
  - Right 50%: Hero image container
    - Image: object-fit contain (shows full image, no crop)
    - Vertically and horizontally centered in container
    - Background: subtle color from config if image doesn't fill
- Mobile hero: Image centered with 24px padding, NOT full-width, natural aspect ratio
- Breadcrumbs below hero
- Content: Centered column, max-width 720px
- Same manual component placement
- End sections same order

**4. GridTemplate.tsx**
- Meta section at top (category, title, author, date) - centered, ABOVE hero grid
- Desktop hero: 4 images in 2x2 grid
  - Fixed aspect ratio: 4:5 (portrait editorial style)
  - object-fit: cover (crops to fill grid cells)
  - Grid gap: 16px
  - Max-width: 1200px, centered
  - Rounded corners on each image
- Mobile hero: 
  - Meta at top
  - Only middle 2 images (images[1] and images[2]) shown
  - Stacked vertically with 16px gap
  - Same 4:5 aspect ratio
  - Centered with 24px side padding
- Breadcrumbs below hero grid
- Content: Centered column, max-width 720px
- Props: `heroImages: string[]` (requires exactly 4 images in frontmatter)
- Same manual component placement
- End sections same order

